// ** Setup **

// OS X Specific:
// Enable command line support:
//     ln -s "/Applications/Sublime Text 2.app/Contents/SharedSupport/bin/subl" /usr/local/bin/subl
// Add the below to your .bashrc:
//     export EDITOR='subl -w'
// Enable key repeating (for Vintage mode):
//     defaults write com.sublimetext.2 ApplePressAndHoldEnabled -bool false

// 1. Install Package Control: http://wbond.net/sublime_packages/package_control
// 2. Via Package Control, install:
//        * Soda Theme
//        * VintageEx
//        * SublimeBlockCursor
// 3. Place this file into */Sublime Text 2/Packages/User
// 4. View -> Hide Minimap

